data.description: Beautifully updated Jackson model boasts four above-grade levels, showcasing light hardwood floors in the living room, lower level, and stairs. The primary bath has been remodeled, the kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances to include a brand new Samsung refrigerator. An adjacent dining room area provides seamless access to a charming small deck, while the living room features a cozy gas fireplace. The full-floor primary suite offers a spa-like bath and a custom organized walk-in closet. On the top level, you'll find two spacious bedrooms, one of which is open to the stairs but can easily be enclosed with drywall and a door. Additional amenities include a one-car garage, extra covered parking space with a storage room, and access to the fantastic Cameron Station amenities.
